projects.name: Malware Probe
projects.description: Malware Analysis Tool to Perform Static Analysis. I contributed to the development of a cutting-edge malware analysis tool known as a 'Malware Probe'. This tool automates static analysis through advanced pattern matching techniques, primarily utilizing YARA rules. My role involved enhancing the tool's capabilities to analyze various file formats such as PDFs, images, APKs, and executables, generating comprehensive reports to aid in threat detection and mitigation.
